/*
  Netlify SPA Routing Configuration
  Redirects all non-matching routes to index.html
  This allows React Router to handle all routing on the client-side
*/

/*  Wildcard redirect for SPA  */
/*  Match any route and serve index.html with 200 status  */
/*  This prevents 404 errors on direct URL access and refresh  */
/*  React Router will handle the routing in the browser  */
/chatbot  /index.html  200
/contact  /index.html  200
/*  Catch-all for any other routes  */
/*  status 200 means the rewrite is internal (not visible to browser)  */
/*  The user sees their URL, not /index.html  */
/  /index.html  200
